<h1>FoodTracker — Support</h1>
<p class="muted">Last updated: 9 June 2026</p>

<p>
Need help with FoodTracker? You're in the right place. FoodTracker is a
nutrition, diet, and calorie tracking app for iOS, developed by Boris
Serzhanovich. Below you'll find answers to common questions and how to reach us.
</p>

<div class="card">
